#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/BBOB-Surrogate.md:1
msgid "BBOB-Surrogate"
msgstr "BBOB-Surrogate"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/BBOB-Surrogate.md:3
msgid ""
"bbob-surrogate includes 72 problem instances, each of which is a surrogate "
"model. In specific, it can be divided into 3 subsets: bbob-surrogate-2D, "
"bbob-surrogate-5D and bbob-surrogate-10D, each of which corresponds to 24 "
"bbob problems. We first train KAN or MLP networks to fit 24 black box "
"functions from bbob, then use the one with more accuracy as the surrogate "
"model. This set is mainly developed for users who aims at exploring the "
"potential of surrogate model in MetaBBO."
msgstr ""
"bbob-surrogate 包含 72 个问题实例，每个实例都是一个代理模型。具体来说，它可以分为 3 个子集：bbob-"
"surrogate-2D、bbob-surrogate-5D 和 bbob-surrogate-10D，每个子集对应 24 个 bbob "
"问题。我们首先训练 KAN 或 MLP 网络来拟合 bbob 中的 24 "
"个黑盒函数，然后使用准确度更高的那个作为代理模型。这个集合主要开发给旨在探索代理模型在 MetaBBO 中潜力的用户。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/BBOB-Surrogate.md:5
msgid ""
"**Paper**：\\ \"[Surrogate Learning in Meta-Black-Box Optimization: A "
"Preliminary Study](https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.18060).\" arXiv preprint "
"arXiv:2503.18060 (2025)."
msgstr ""
"**论文**：\\\"[Surrogate Learning in Meta-Black-Box Optimization: A "
"Preliminary Study](https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.18060).\" arXiv preprint "
"arXiv:2503.18060 (2025)."

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/BBOB-Surrogate.md:7
msgid ""
"**Code Resource**： [BBOB-Surrogate](https://github.com/GMC-DRL/Surr-RLDE)"
msgstr "**代码资源**： [BBOB-Surrogate](https://github.com/GMC-DRL/Surr-RLDE)"

