msgid "Fully-separable functions (F1-F3)"
msgstr "完全可分离函数（F1-F3）"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013LSGO.md:10
msgid "Two types of partially separable functions:"
msgstr "两种部分可分离函数："

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013LSGO.md:11
msgid ""
"Partially separable functions with a set of non-separable subcomponents and "
"one fully-separable subcomponents (F4-F7)"
msgstr "具有一组不可分离子组件和一个完全可分离子组件的部分可分离函数（F4-F7）"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013LSGO.md:12
