msgid "Overlapping functions with conflicting subcomponents (F14)"
msgstr "存在具有冲突子组件的重叠函数（F14）"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013LSGO.md:16
msgid "Fully-nonseparable functions (F15)"
msgstr "完全非可分离函数（F15）"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013LSGO.md:18
msgid ""
"Except for F13 and F14, which are 905-dimensional, the dimensions of other "
