msgstr "除了 F13 和 F14 是 905 维的，其他问题的维度都是 1000。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:1
msgid "CEC2013MMO"
msgstr "CEC2013MMO"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:2
msgid ""
"CEC2013MMO is based on CEC2013LSGO benchmark and specially crafeted for "
"multi-modal optimization, which includes 20 synthetic problem instances "
"covering various dimensions (1D~20D), each with varied number of (1 ~ 216) "
"global optima. Among them, F1 to F5 are simple uni-modal functions, F6 to "
"F10 are dimension-scalable functions with multiple global optima, and F11 to"
" F20 are complex composition functions with challenging landscapes."
msgstr ""
"CEC2013MMO 基于 CEC2013LSGO 基线，专门为多模态优化而设计，包含 20 "
"个合成问题实例，涵盖各种维度（1D~20D），每个实例具有不同数量的全局最优解（1 ~ 216）。其中，F1 到 F5 是简单的单模态函数，F6 到 "
"F10 是具有多个全局最优解的维度可扩展函数，F11 到 F20 是具有挑战性景观的复杂组合函数。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:4
msgid ""
"Paper：\"[Benchmark functions for CEC’2013 special session and competition on"
" niching methods for multimodal function "
"optimization.](https://web.xidian.edu.cn/xlwang/files/20150312_175833.pdf)\""
" RMIT University, evolutionary computation and machine learning Group, "
"Australia, Tech. Rep (2013)."
msgstr ""
"论文：\\\"[Benchmark functions for CEC’2013 special session and competition on"
" niching methods for multimodal function "
"optimization.](https://web.xidian.edu.cn/xlwang/files/20150312_175833.pdf)\""
" RMIT University, evolutionary computation and machine learning Group, "
"Australia, Tech. Rep (2013)."

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:5
msgid "Code Resource： [CEC2013MMO](https://github.com/mikeagn/CEC2013)"
msgstr "代码资源：[CEC2013MMO](https://github.com/mikeagn/CEC2013)"

