msgid ""
"Original tasks are maximization; **converted to minimization** via sign "
"flip."
msgstr "原始任务为最大化；通过符号翻转将其**转换为最小化**。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:10
msgid "Covers 1D to 20D settings with varying numbers of optima."
msgstr "涵盖1D到20D的设置，具有不同数量的最优解。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:12
msgid "Function Summary"
msgstr "函数摘要"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:101
msgid "Dataset Setup"
msgstr "数据集设置"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:103
msgid ""
"The parameter settings used for each problem are as follows. **Note again** "
"that here we reformulate the origin problems as minimization problems in the"
" dataset setting by applying negative signs to the evaluation results of the"
" original functions."
msgstr ""
"每个问题使用的参数设置如下。**再次注意**，在这里我们将原始问题重新表述为数据集中以最小化为目标的优化问题，通过在原始函数的评估结果上应用负号来实现。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:259
msgid "Evaluation Metrics"
msgstr "评估指标"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:261
#, python-format
msgid "**Peak Ratio (PR)**: Measures average % of known optima found."
msgstr "**峰比（PR）**: 衡量已知最优解找到的平均百分比。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:262
#, python-format
msgid "**Success Rate (SR)**: % of runs that find *all* global optima."
msgstr "**成功率（SR）**：找到所有全局最优解的运行次数的百分比。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:263
msgid "Both metrics use ε = 1e-4 as the primary accuracy threshold."
msgstr "两种指标都使用 ε = 1e-4 作为主要准确度阈值。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:265
msgid "Max Function Evaluations (MaxFEs)"
msgstr "最大函数评估次数 (MaxFEs)"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:290
msgid "Train-Test Split"
msgstr "训练-测试分割"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:292
msgid "Based on difficulty from empirical studies:"
msgstr "根据实证研究中的难度："

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:294
msgid "**Easy Problems**: P1–P7, P10–P12"
msgstr "**简单问题**：P1–P7，P10–P12"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2013MMO.md:295
msgid "**Difficult Problems**: P8–P9, P13–P20"
msgstr "**困难问题**: P8–P9, P13–P20"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:1
msgid "CEC2017MTO"
msgstr "CEC2017MTO"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:3
msgid ""
"CEC2017MTO comprises 9 multi-task problem instances, each of which contains "
"two basic problems. Optional basic problems include Shpere, Rosenbrock, "
"Ackley, Rastrigin, Griewank, Weierstrass and Schwefel, with dimension "
"ranging from 25D~50D."
msgstr ""
"CEC2017MTO 包含 9 个多任务问题实例，每个实例包含两个基本问题。可选的基本问题包括 "
"Sphere、Rosenbrock、Ackley、Rastrigin、Griewank、Weierstrass 和 Schwefel，维度范围从 "
"25D~50D。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:5
msgid ""
"Paper：\"[Evolutionary multitasking for single-objective continuous "
"optimization: Benchmark problems, performance metric, and baseline "
"results.](https://arxiv.org/abs/1706.03470)\" arXiv preprint "
"arXiv:1706.03470 (2017)."
msgstr ""
"论文：\\\"[Evolutionary multitasking for single-objective continuous "
"optimization: Benchmark problems, performance metric, and baseline "
"results.](https://arxiv.org/abs/1706.03470)\" arXiv preprint "
"arXiv:1706.03470 (2017)."

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:6
msgid ""
"Code Resource： [CEC2017MTO](http://www.bdsc.site/websites/MTO/index.html)"
msgstr "代码资源：[CEC2017MTO](http://www.bdsc.site/websites/MTO/index.html)"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:7
#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/WCCI2020.md:7
msgid "Details"
msgstr "细节"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:12
msgid ""
"In MetaBox, we give three benchmark split difficulty mode of both train and "
"test from the nine tasks of CEC2017 as **easy**, **difficult** and **full**."
" The benchmark split criterion is according to the complexity of degree of "
"intersection and inter-task similarity."
msgstr ""
"在MetaBox中，我们从CEC2017的九个任务中为训练和测试提供了三种基线分割难度模式，分别为**easy**、**difficult**和**full**。基线分割标准是根据交集的复杂程度和跨任务相似性。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:13
msgid "**\"easy\"**:  train:[1,2,3,4,5,6] test:[7,8,9]"
msgstr "**\"easy\"**: 训练:[1,2,3,4,5,6] 测试:[7,8,9]"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:14
msgid "**\"difficult\"**:  train:[7,8,9] test:[1,2,3,4,5,6]"
msgstr "**\"difficult\"**: 训练:[7,8,9] 测试:[1,2,3,4,5,6]"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/CEC2017MTO.md:15
msgid "**\"full\"**:  train:[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9]  test:[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9]"
msgstr "**\"full\"**: 训练：[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9]  测试：[1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9]"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/COCO-BBOB.md:1
msgid "COCO-BBOB"
msgstr "COCO-BBOB"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/COCO-BBOB.md:3
msgid ""
"The blackbox optimization benchmarking (bbob) test suite is COCO's standard "
"test suite with 24 noiseless, single-objective and scalable test functions. "
"Each function is provided in dimensions (2, 3, 5, 10, 20, 40) and in 15 "
"instances, however also available for arbitrary dimensions and number of "
"instances. Links to their definition with visualizations are provided in the"
" table."
msgstr ""
"黑盒优化基线测试（bbob）测试套件是COCO的标准测试套件，包含24个无噪声、单目标和可扩展的测试函数。每个函数提供在维度（2, 3, 5, 10, "
"20, 40）下的15个实例，但也支持任意维度和数量的实例。表格中提供了它们定义及可视化的链接。"

