#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/HPO-B.md:1
msgid "HPO-B"
msgstr "HPO-B"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/HPO-B.md:3
msgid ""
"HPO-B is an autoML hyper-parameter optimization benchmark which includes a "
"wide range of hyperparameter optimization tasks for 16 different model types"
" (e.g., SVM, XGBoost, etc.), resulting in a total of 935 problem instances. "
"The dimension of these problem instances range from 2 to 16. We also note "
"that HPO-B represents problems with ill-conditioned landscape such as huge "
"flattern."
msgstr ""
"HPO-B 是一个 autoML 超参数优化基线，它包含多种超参数优化任务，适用于 16 种不同的模型类型（例如，SVM、XGBoost 等），共计 "
"935 个问题实例。这些问题实例的维度范围从 2 到 16。我们还注意到，HPO-B 代表具有不良条件地形的问题，例如巨大的平坦区域。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/HPO-B.md:5
msgid ""
"**Paper**：\"[Hpo-b: A large-scale reproducible benchmark for black-box hpo "
"based on openml.](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2106.06257)\" arXiv preprint "
"arXiv:2106.06257 (2021)."
msgstr ""
"**论文**：\\\"[Hpo-b: A large-scale reproducible benchmark for black-box hpo "
"based on openml.](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2106.06257)\" arXiv preprint "

