"MOO-Synthetic is constructed by mixing 4 well-known multi-objective problem "
"sets: ZDT, UF, DTLZ and WFG. In total, we have constructed 187 problem "
"instances. Their objective numbers range from 2 \\~ 10, dimensions range "
"from 6D \\~ 38D."
