#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/Neuroevolution.md:3
msgid ""
"This problem set is based on the neuroevolution interfaces in <a "
"href=\"https://evox.readthedocs.io/en/latest/examples/brax.html\">EvoX</a>. "
"The goal is to optimize the parameters of neural network-based RL agents for"
" a series of Robotic Control tasks. We pre-define 11 control tasks (e.g., "
"swimmer, ant, walker2D etc.), and 6 MLP structures with 0~5 hidden layers. "
"The combinations of task & network structure result in 66 problem instances,"
" which feature extremely high-dimensional problems (>=1000D)."
msgstr ""
"这个问题集基于 <a "
"href=\"https://evox.readthedocs.io/en/latest/examples/brax.html\">EvoX</a>"
" 中的神经进化接口。目标是通过优化基于神经网络的强化学习智能体的参数来应对一系列机器人控制任务。我们预先定义了 11 "
"个控制任务（例如，游泳者、蚂蚁、2D 行走者等），以及 6 种具有 0~5 个隐藏层的 MLP 结构。任务与网络结构的组合产生了 66 "
"个问题实例，这些实例具有极高的维度（>=1000D）。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/Neuroevolution.md:5
msgid ""
"**Paper**：\"[EvoX: A distributed GPU-accelerated framework for scalable "
"evolutionary "
"computation.](https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/10499977)\" IEEE"
" Transactions on Evolutionary Computation (2024)."
msgstr ""
"**论文**：\\\"[EvoX: "
"一个可扩展的分布式GPU加速进化计算框架。](https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/10499977)\\\""
" IEEE Transactions on Evolutionary Computation (2024)."

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/Neuroevolution.md:6
msgid "**Code Resource**： [NE](https://github.com/EMI-Group/evox)"
msgstr "**代码资源**： [NE](https://github.com/EMI-Group/evox)"

