msgid "Problem Sets"
msgstr "问题集"


#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/Protein-Docking.md:3
msgid ""
"Protein-Docking benchmark, where the objective is to minimize the Gibbs free"
" energy resulting from protein-protein interaction between a given complex "
"and any other conformation. We select 28 protein complexes and randomly "
"initialize 10 starting points for each complex, resulting in 280 problem "
"instances. To simplify the problem structure, we only optimize 12 "
"interaction points in a complex instance (12D problem)."
msgstr ""
"蛋白质对接基线测试，其目标是使给定复合物与其他构象之间蛋白质-"
"蛋白质相互作用的吉布斯自由能最小化。我们选择了28个蛋白质复合物，并为每个复合物随机初始化10个起始点，从而产生280个问题实例。为了简化问题结构，我们在复合物实例中仅优化12个相互作用点（12D问题）。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/Protein-Docking.md:5
msgid ""
"**Paper**：\"[Protein–protein docking benchmark version "
"4.0.](https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/prot.22830)\" "
"Proteins: Structure, Function, and Bioinformatics 78.15 (2010): 3111-3114."
msgstr ""
"**论文**：\\\"[蛋白质-蛋白质对接基线测试版本 "
"4.0.](https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1002/prot.22830)\\\" "
"Proteins: Structure, Function, and Bioinformatics 78.15 (2010): 3111-3114."

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/Protein-Docking.md:6
msgid ""
"**Code Resource**： [Protein-Docking](https://zlab.wenglab.org/benchmark/)"
msgstr "**代码资源**： [蛋白质对接](https://zlab.wenglab.org/benchmark/)"

