msgid "Single-Object Optimization"
msgstr "单目标优化"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/UAV.md:3
msgid ""
"UAV provides 56 terrain-based landscapes as realistic Unmanned Aerial "
"Vehicle(UAV) path planning problems, each of which is 30D. The objective is "
"to select given number of path nodes (x,y,z coordinates) from the 3D space, "
"so the the UAV could fly as shortly as possible in a collision-free way."
msgstr ""
"UAV 提供 56 个基于地形的地形图，作为逼真的无人机(UAV)路径规划问题，每个问题都是 30 维的。目标是选择给定数量的路径节点（x,y,z "
"坐标）从 3D 空间中，以便无人机能够以无碰撞的方式尽可能短地飞行。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/UAV.md:5
msgid ""
"**Paper**：\"[Benchmarking global optimization techniques for unmanned aerial"
" vehicle path planning.](https://arxiv.org/abs/2501.14503)\" arXiv preprint "
"arXiv:2501.14503 (2025)."
msgstr ""
"**论文**：\\\"[Benchmarking global optimization techniques for unmanned aerial "
"vehicle path planning.](https://arxiv.org/abs/2501.14503)\\\" arXiv 预印本 "
"arXiv:2501.14503 (2025)."

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/UAV.md:6
msgid "**Code Resource**： [UAV](https://zenodo.org/records/12793991)"
msgstr "**代码资源**： [UAV](https://zenodo.org/records/12793991)"

