msgid ""
"Selected from **5,000 automatically generated terrains**, with **56 diverse "
"terrains** carefully chosen for their complexity and real-world resemblance."
msgstr "从**5,000个自动生成的地形**中选出，并**56个具有多样性的地形**经过精心挑选，因其复杂性和与现实世界的相似性。"

