#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/WCCI2020.md:1
msgid "WCCI2020"
msgstr "WCCI2020"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/WCCI2020.md:3
msgid ""
"WCCI2020 comprises 10 multi-task problem instances, each of which contains "
"50 basic problems. Optional basic problems include Shpere, Rosenbrock, "
"Ackley, Rastrigin, Griewank, Weierstrass and Schwefel, which are all 50D."
msgstr ""
"WCCI2020 包含 10 个多任务问题实例，每个实例包含 50 个基本问题。可选的基本问题包括 "
"Sphere、Rosenbrock、Ackley、Rastrigin、Griewank、Weierstrass 和 Schwefel，这些都是 50D "
"的。"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/WCCI2020.md:5
msgid ""
"Paper：[WCCI2020](http://www.bdsc.site/websites/MTO_competition_2020/MTO_Competition_WCCI_2020.html)"
msgstr ""
"论文：[WCCI2020](http://www.bdsc.site/websites/MTO_competition_2020/MTO_Competition_WCCI_2020.html)"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/WCCI2020.md:6
