"Code Resource： [WCCI2020](http://www.bdsc.site/websites/MTO/index.html)"
msgstr "代码资源：[WCCI2020](http://www.bdsc.site/websites/MTO/index.html)"

#: ../../source/guide/DS_BL/WCCI2020.md:12
msgid ""
"In MetaBox, we give three benchmark split difficulty mode of both train and "
"test from the ten tasks of WCCI2020 as **easy**, **difficult** and **full**."
" The benchmark split criterion is according to the richness of the "
"composition of the basic functions."
msgstr ""
"在MetaBox中，我们从WCCI2020的十个任务中为训练和测试提供了三种基线分割难度模式，分别为**easy**、**difficult**和**full**。基线分割标准是根据基本函数组成的丰富性。"

