#: ../../source/guide/QuickStart/Running Logic.md:1
msgid "Running Logic"
msgstr "运行逻辑"

#: ../../source/guide/QuickStart/Running Logic.md:2
msgid ""
"Based on MetaBox’s fully automatic train-test-log workflow, **Unification, "
"Efficiency and Flexible** are the core concepts of MetaBox-v2.0"
msgstr "基于MetaBox的完全自动训练-测试-日志工作流，**统一、高效和灵活**是MetaBox-v2.0的核心概念。"

#: ../../source/guide/QuickStart/Running Logic.md:3
msgid ""
"**Unification:** MetaBox-v2.0 provides a unified interface for various "
"MetaBBO (MetaBBO-RL、MetaBBO-SL、MetaBBO-ICL、MetaBBO-NE) and test suites for "
"different types of problems."
msgstr ""
"**统一性：** MetaBox-v2.0 提供了一个统一的接口，用于各种 MetaBBO（MetaBBO-RL、MetaBBO-SL、MetaBBO-"
"ICL、MetaBBO-NE）以及不同类型问题的测试套件。"

#: ../../source/guide/QuickStart/Running Logic.md:4
msgid ""
"**Efficiency:**  Parallelization enables MetaBox-v2.0 to train and test "
"efficiently. As the first development exemplar to enable parallel training "
"for MetaBBO, MetaBox-v2.0 supports training speeds up to 10 times faster "
"than MetaBox-v1.0. Various Ray-based parallel modes allow users to fully "
"utilize their computing resources to accelerate testing."
msgstr ""
"**效率：** 并行化使 MetaBox-v2.0 能够高效地训练和测试。作为首个支持 MetaBBO 并行训练的开发范例，MetaBox-v2.0 "
"支持比 MetaBox-v1.0 快 10 倍的训练速度。多种基于 Ray 的并行模式允许用户充分利用其计算资源来加速测试。"

#: ../../source/guide/QuickStart/Running Logic.md:5
msgid ""
"**Flexible:** Taking the provided Evaluation Metrics as an example, by "
"recording Metadata, users can easily and flexibly visualize these evaluation"
" metrics across different MetaBBO methods for various types of problems, "
"without being constrained by specific problems or approaches. There are even"
" more flexible usages, including but not limited to leveraging existing "
"resources from other platforms (such as EvoX) to extend MetaBox’s current "
"methods and problem sets. For more information, please refer to the Gallery!"
msgstr ""
"**灵活:** "
"以提供的评估指标为例，通过记录元数据，用户可以轻松灵活地跨不同的MetaBBO方法可视化这些评估指标，而不会受到特定问题或方法的限制。还有更灵活的使用方式，包括但不限于利用其他平台（如EvoX）的现有资源来扩展MetaBox的当前方法和问题集。更多详情，请参考Gallery！"

#: ../../source/guide/QuickStart/Running Logic.md:7
msgid ""
"Based on the above three features, users only need to specify the target "
"problem and the MetaBBO algorithm to be used. MetaBox will then provide "
"fully automated training and testing, and ultimately allow flexible "
"visualization of results using the recorded Metadata."
msgstr ""
"基于上述三个特性，用户只需指定目标问题和要使用的MetaBBO算法。MetaBox将提供全自动的训练和测试，并最终允许用户使用记录的Metadata对结果进行灵活的可视化。"

