#: ../../source/index.md:64
msgid ""
"we propose MetaBox 2.0 version (MetaBox-v2) as a major upgradation of "
"[MetaBox-v1](https://github.com/MetaEvo/MetaBox/tree/v1.0.0). MetaBox-v2 now"
" supports plentiful optimization scenarios to embrace users from single-"
"objective optimization, multi-objective optimization, multi-modal "
"optimization, multi-task optimization and etc. Correspondingly, **18 "
"optimization problem sets** (synthetic + realistic), **1900+ problem "
"instances** and **36 baseline methods** (traditional optimizers + up-to-date"
" MetaBBOs) are reproduced within MetaBox-v2 to assist various research ideas"
" and comprehensive comparison. To address MetaBBO's inherent efficiency "
"issue, we have optimized low-level implementation of MetaBox-v2 to support "
"parallel meta-training and evaluation, which reduces the running cost from "
"days to hours. More importantly, we have optimized MetaBox-v2's sourcecode "
"to support **sufficient development flexbility**, with clear and sound "
"tutotials correspondingly. Enjoy your journey of learning and using MetaBBO "
"from here!"
msgstr ""
"我们提出了 MetaBox 2.0 版本（MetaBox-v2）作为 "
"[MetaBox-v1](https://github.com/MetaEvo/MetaBox/tree/v1.0.0) "
"的重要升级。MetaBox-v2 现在支持丰富的优化场景，以涵盖从单目标优化、多目标优化、多模态优化、多任务优化等等的用户。相应地，**18 "
"个优化问题集**（合成 + 真实）、**1900+ 问题实例**和**36 个基线方法**（传统优化器 + 最新的 MetaBBOs）在 "
"MetaBox-v2 中被复现，以协助各种研究思路和全面比较。为了解决 MetaBBO 的固有效率问题，我们对 MetaBox-v2 "
"的底层实现进行了优化，以支持并行元训练和评估，将运行成本从天缩短到小时。更重要的是，我们对 MetaBox-v2 "
"的源代码进行了优化，以支持**足够的开发灵活性**，并提供了清晰且完善的教程。从这里开始，享受学习和使用 MetaBBO 的旅程吧！"

